const api = 'https://frontend-take-home.fetchrewards.com/form'

export const getOccupcations = () => 
    fetch(`${api}`)
        .then(res => res.json)
        .then(data => data.occupcations)


export const getStates = () => 
    fetch(`${api}`)
        .then(res => res.json)
        .then(data => data.states)
        .catch(error => {
            console.log(error)
        })


export const postForm = (formData) =>
  fetch(`${api}`, {
    method: 'POST',
  }).then(res => res.json())
